## API Reference

| Method | Path | Auth | Description |
|--------|------|------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/api/v1/` | No | Service running status |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/info` | No | App title, version, description |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/health/live` | No | Kubernetes liveness probe |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/health/ready` | No | Kubernetes readiness probe (DB ping) |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/items` | Yes | List items (paginated, filtered, sorted) |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/items` | Yes | Create a new item |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/items/{id}` | Yes | Get item by ID |
| `PATCH` | `/api/v1/items/{id}` | Yes | Partial update |
| `DELETE` | `/api/v1/items/{id}` | Yes | Delete item |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/tasks` | Yes | Enqueue a background task |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/tasks/{id}` | Yes | Get task status |
| `DELETE` | `/api/v1/tasks/{id}` | Yes | Cancel a pending task |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/admin/log-level` | No | Override log level at runtime |

